Package: wikkitidy
Title: Tidy analysis of Wikipedia in R 
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Falk", , "michaelgfalk@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9261-8390"))
Description: A wrapper around Wikipedia's major APIs: the MediaWiki Action API,
    REST API and Wikmedia REST API. These three APIs provide complementary
    functionality for the analysis of Wikipedia by social scientists and digital
    humanists. This package provides a tidy interface to all three APIs, along
    with a range of functions that solve common tasks in Wikipedia research.
